### Create YouTube landscape video
POST http://localhost:3000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

{
  "script": "Neste vídeo vamos explorar como a inteligência artificial está revolucionando o mundo moderno. Desde diagnósticos médicos até carros autônomos, a IA já faz parte do nosso cotidiano.",
  "language": "pt",
  "videoItems": [
    {
      "searchTerm": "inteligencia artificial futuro",
      "type": "video",
      "displayMode": "fit"
    },
    {
      "searchTerm": "neural network diagram",
      "type": "image",
      "displayMode": "ken_burns"
    },
    {
      "searchTerm": "Inteligência Artificial",
      "type": "animated_text",
      "displayMode": "typewriter"
    }
  ],
  "useSrt": true,
  "srtStyle": {
    "position": "bottom",
    "backgroundColor": "#0066ff",
    "fontSize": 52,
    "fontFamily": "Inter"
  },
  "useBackgroundMusic": true,
  "backgroundMusicStyle": "hopeful",
  "config": {
    "orientation": "landscape",
    "paddingBack": 1500,
    "musicVolume": "medium"
  }
}

###

### Create YouTube Shorts (portrait) video
POST http://localhost:3000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

{
  "script": "Did you know that E equals mc squared means energy equals mass times the speed of light squared?",
  "language": "en",
  "videoItems": [
    {
      "searchTerm": "physics science laboratory",
      "type": "video"
    },
    {
      "searchTerm": "E = mc²",
      "type": "formula",
      "displayMode": "reveal"
    }
  ],
  "useSrt": true,
  "useBackgroundMusic": true,
  "backgroundMusicStyle": "contemplative",
  "config": {
    "orientation": "portrait",
    "musicVolume": "low"
  }
}

###

### Check video status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos/{{videoId}}/status
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

###

### List all videos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

###

### Download video
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos/{{videoId}}
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

###

### Delete video
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/videos/{{videoId}}
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

###

### List music styles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos/music-styles
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

###

### Health check (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Swagger docs (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:3000/docs
